text.tspan: Average daily time spent by women on domestic work (paid and
Average daily number of hours spent on paid and unpaid domestic work combined (total work burden). The average is
taken with respect to the entire relevant population, including those who devote no time to domestic work.
Data source: UN Minimum Set of Gender Indicators (2017)
